org.cef.handler

Class CefMessageRouterHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.callback.CefNativeAdapter
      • org.cef.handler.CefMessageRouterHandlerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CefNative, CefMessageRouterHandler 

    public abstract class CefMessageRouterHandlerAdapter
extends CefNativeAdapter
implements CefMessageRouterHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving message router events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects.(用于接收消息路由器事件的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类的存在是为了方便创建处理程序对象。)

      • onQuery

        public boolean onQuery(CefBrowser browser,
                       CefFrame frame,
                       long queryId,
                       java.lang.String request,
                       boolean persistent,
                       CefQueryCallback callback)
        Description copied from interface: CefMessageRouterHandler
        Called when the browser receives a JavaScript query.(当浏览器接收到JavaScript查询时调用。)
        Specified by:
        onQuery in interface CefMessageRouterHandler
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        queryId - The unique ID for the query.(queryId-查询的唯一ID。)
        persistent - True if the query is persistent.(persistent-如果查询是持久的，则为True。)
        callback - Object used to continue or cancel the query asynchronously.(callback-用于异步继续或取消查询的对象。)
        Returns:
        True to handle the query or false to propagate the query to other registered handlers, if any. If no handlers return true from this method then the query will be automatically canceled with an error code of -1 delivered to the JavaScript onFailure callback.(True用于处理查询，false用于将查询传播到其他已注册的处理程序（如果有的话）。如果此方法没有处理程序返回true，那么查询将自动取消，并将错误代码-1传递给JavaScript的onFailure回调。)
